### Implement HTTP redirect response with Fastify

Source: https://github.com/nestjs/docs.nestjs.com/blob/master/content/techniques/performance.md

TypeScript decorator-based code demonstrating proper redirect handling in Fastify. Unlike Express, Fastify requires both the status code (302) and redirect URL to be specified. The method receives the response object and uses status() and redirect() methods.

```typescript
