### Set Job Priority in BullMQ Queue

Source: https://github.com/nestjs/docs.nestjs.com/blob/master/content/techniques/queues.md

Demonstrates how to assign a priority level to a job using the priority option. Priority values range from 1 (highest) to MAX_INT (lowest). Higher priority jobs are processed first, but using priorities has a slight performance impact.

```typescript
